---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import installData from '../data/installs/car-cameras.json';
import ImgCard from '../components/ImgCard.astro';
const { install } = installData;
const title = 'GPS Tracking and Fleet Management Systems';
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <main>
    <div class="container fade-in">
      <section>
        <h1 class="display-6 mb-5">{title}</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-5">
          Do you own a fleet of vehicles driven by employees, or just want to know where your
          teenager is? Tracking systems can cover real-time or downloadable information letting you
          know when the vehicle was driven, where it went, how fast it went, where it stopped and
          anything else you desire. The real-time or active systems can also help in case a vehicle
          is stolen or driven beyond a designated perimeter. This is called "Geofencing".
        </p>
